<font face="Impress BT" size="83">The position of chairman always rotates.</font>

500
00:28:52,250 --> 00:28:53,870
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Who is it this time?</font>

501
00:28:54,870 --> 00:28:56,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">That would be me!</font>

502
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:58,630
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Everyone, it will be my honor.</font>

503
00:28:58,630 --> 00:29:00,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Ballywood, huh?</font>

504
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:02,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Sounds good.</font>

505
00:29:02,050 --> 00:29:05,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">This should run smoothly, then.</font>

506
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:09,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Even if we have a full seven days,
we have so much to address.</font>

507
00:29:09,220 --> 00:29:12,770
<font face="Impress BT" size="84"><i>This is the great conference 
that determines the order of the world.</i></font>

508
00:29:13,430 --> 00:29:16,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="84"><i>It is known as...</i></font>

509
00:29:17,650 --> 00:29:21,860
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Well then... my fellow monarchs...</font>

510
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:29,280
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">let us carefully discuss 
the future of this beautiful world!</font>

511
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:35,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="84"><i>the Reverie!</i></font>

512
00:29:36,670 --> 00:29:39,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">And so the conference begins.</font>

513
00:29:39,840 --> 00:29:46,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Apparently, King Cobra of Arabasta
is requesting an audience with us.</font>

514
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:48,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">The Nefertari family</font>

515
00:29:48,890 --> 00:29:52,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">was the only family 
of the First Twenty</font>

516
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:55,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">that stayed in the lower realm 
800 years ago.</font>

517
00:29:55,640 --> 00:30:00,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">In a sense, they're traitors.
Has he noticed something?</font>

518
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:03,530
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Let's hope he doesn't
complicate matters.</font>

519
00:30:03,530 --> 00:30:07,660
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">You could say the same
about the situation with Big Mom and Kaido.</font>

520
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:13,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">It's been two years since the Summit War.
 And yet, this maelstrom will not cease.</font>

521
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:18,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">This world's equilibrium 
cannot be maintained indefinitely.</font>

522
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:24,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">The time has come 
for a great cleansing.</font>

523
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:36,560
<font face="Roboto" size="56"><font size="60"><font color="#000000">The Chamber of Flowers
Pangaea Castle</font></font></font>

