00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,520
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Lord Imu.</font>

526
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:40,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">The Five Elders have arrived.</font>

527
00:31:37,950 --> 00:31:42,580
<font face="Impress BT" size="83">Have you discovered another light 
